QuestData.Title: Someone's Missing Axe
QuestData.Description: <A throwing axe of frostwolf make is sticking out of the side of this talbuk. Perhaps Stalker Ogka will be interested in your find.>
QuestData.LogDescription: Take the Frostwolf Axe to Stalker Ogka at Wor'var.
QuestData.RewardText: That's MY axe! Where'd you get it?
